<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Error 500 – Internal Server Error</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: sans-serif;
        background: hsl(50, 40%, 97%);
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 1.5em;
      }
      article {
        max-width: 80ch;
        margin: 20vh auto 0;
        font-size: 1.25em;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <article>
      <h1>500 – Internal Server Error</h1>
      <p>
        We failed to serve the URL <code><%= @conn.request_path %></code>, please retry in a moment.
      </p>
      <p>
        If the problem persists, we would appreciate that you <a
          href={"https://airtable.com/shrTzTwby7JhFEqi6?prefill_Page=" <> @conn.request_path}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer external"
        >
        contact us
        </a>.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: min(15vh, 4em)">Go to <a href="/">Risteys home page</a>.</p>
    </article>
  </body>
</html>
